<p>Comments containing the following will not be published or will be edited:</p>
<ul class="nhsuk-list nhsuk-list--bullet">
<li>Names of individuals, mention of gender or identifying features</li>
<li>Offensive, abusive or inappropriate language or remark</li>
<li>Complaints relating to clinical negligence which should first be addressed by the relevant hospital or practice</li>
</ul>
<p>We recommend you read the complete <a href="https://www.nhs.uk/our-policies/comments-policy/" id="moderation-rules">moderation rules</a> before proceeding.</p>
<div class="nhsuk-inset-text">
<span class="nhsuk-u-visually-hidden">Information: </span>
<h2>Coronavirus</h2>
<p>When leaving your review, please be aware that our NHS staff are under considerable pressure during the Coronavirus (COVID-19) outbreak.</p>
<p>Any feedback that may cause patients to reconsider using a health provider's service will be looked at more closely than usual and may be rejected.</p>
<p>Also, please be aware that many health services are extremely busy dealing with coronavirus. This is affecting the way they're able to deliver services, and it may mean it's not possible for them to respond to your review. Thank you for your understanding at this difficult time.</p>
</div>
